      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-09-04/columbus-stops-cyber-researcher-from-flagging-stolen-police-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
